Marking the 2019 edition of the World Economic Forum on Africa, Old Mutual will explore the future of financial services in Africa. SPONSORED CONTENT JOHANNESBURG - Old Mutual will host a Youth Panel discussion at 7pm on Tuesday night, ahead of the World Economic Forum on Africa. The panelists will focus on issues including: - How will tech help or hinder our progress in the 4IR? - What are the latest trends and how best to prepare for the future? - The role of youth in shaping financial services into the future. 